    "Summaries": {
        "eng": "A remote island slightly south of Honshu. The dormitory \"Tsugumi Dormitory\", which was renovated from the old school building, was home to Wataru Hoshino, the only male dormitory student, and several female dormitory students as the number of dormitory students decreased. The dormitory is rumored to be a nautical harem by the islanders. Transfer students who came during this period are also involved, and while sometimes repelling, they spend happy days.",
        "jpn": "本州から少し南にある離島。学園の旧校舎を改装した寮“つぐみ寮”は、寮生の減少にともない、唯一の男子寮生である星野航と、数人の女子寮生たちが住んでいた。その寮は島の住人からは航のハーレムだと噂されている。この時期にやってきた転校生も巻き込み、時には反発したりしながらも楽しい毎日を過ごしていく…。"
    },
